#: src/04-configuration.md:11
msgid "Three ways to set a value"
msgstr ""

#: src/04-configuration.md:13
msgid ""
"Every setting can be defined directly in TOML, via an environment variable, "
"or via Vault:"
msgstr ""

#: src/04-configuration.md:15
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"# Directly in the file (fine for development)\n"
"tokenSecret = \"my-secret\"\n"
"\n"
"# From an environment variable\n"
"tokenSecret = { env = \"MYC_TOKEN_SECRET\" }\n"
"\n"
"# From HashiCorp Vault (recommended for production)\n"
"tokenSecret = { vault = { path = \"myc/core/accountLifeCycle\", key = "
"\"tokenSecret\" } }\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/04-configuration.md:26
msgid ""
"Vault values are resolved at runtime — you don't need to restart after "
"changing a secret in Vault."
msgstr ""

