msgid ""
"```\n"
"Event fires inside Mycelium\n"
"  │\n"
"  ▼\n"
"Webhook dispatcher looks up registered listeners for this event type\n"
"  │\n"
"  ▼\n"
"POST <webhook_url>\n"
"Content-Type: application/json\n"
"{ \"event\": \"userAccount.created\", \"payload\": { ... } }\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

